Motif-Index of Folk-Literature — JSON Data
============================================

This directory contains data derived from:

  Repository: https://github.com/fbkarsdorp/tmi
  Author:     Folgert Karsdorp
  License:    Apache License 2.0 (see LICENSE in this directory)

The data is a JSON digitization of Stith Thompson's Motif-Index of
Folk-Literature (1955–1958), a standard reference work in folklore studies.

The original JSON was restructured into per-category files for this project.
No motif content was added, removed, or altered.
